_aChangeLog.text: added missing teleports. If you already downloaded this map, please delete it and download again.

_sText:
After years of inactivity, here's one of my first project since then! The follow up to surf_hyper.

5 stages and 1 bonus.
Bonus entry can be found at stage 2 start.

I hope it is a nice fresh breeze of air in the current surf meta :)

The map is designed for surftimer servers. Noblock required and surf timer mods highly advised.
Feel free to make a showcase video! Hit me up and I will link it here and credit you.
Max velocity is 3500
